# AI Trading Arena — UI Design System

## Aesthetic

- **Clean editorial / Claude-inspired**: warm white `#faf9f5`, sharp corners (`border-radius: 0`), thin borders
- **No vibecoded UI**: no neon, no glows, no gradients on text, no dark mode, no glass blur
- **Typography**: Instrument Serif (titles), DM Sans (body), JetBrains Mono (data/charts)
- **Accent**: terracotta `#c96442` sparingly; black `#1a1a1a` for primary actions
- **Reference**: Alpha Arena by Nof1 — ticker, tabs, ModelChat, update banners

## Interactivity (keep)

- Hover tooltips on stat tiles and asset chips
- Charts: IndexChart, Sparkline, ModelPnLChart (recharts, muted palette via `lib/chart-theme.ts`)
- Position heatmap, model battle, live polling

## Shell

Every page uses `Shell`: Header + TabTickerBar + content.

## Do not

- Rounded corners, neon green, purple glows, gradient headlines
- Dark backgrounds or crypto-bro copy ("deploy paper", "LIVE ARENA")
- Hardcode chart colors — use `CHART` from `lib/chart-theme.ts`
